    public static class CalendarSwap.TimeMedium
extends CalendarSwap
    Transforms Calendars to DateFormat.MEDIUM time strings.
    Example output:
    • "10:11:12 AM" // en_US
    • "10:11:12" // ja_JP
    • "오전 10:11:12" // ko_KR
